<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Expend" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Expend,</orth> to spend, to waste, to give away: <emph>I would e. it</emph> (my life) <cit><quote>with all willingness,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.150" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 150</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to e. your time with us,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 23</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.3.391" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 3, 391</bibl>. <cit><quote>riches . . careless heirs may e.</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 3.2.29" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. III, 2, 29</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>